<F P=100> Laos </F>
<H3> <TI>   Vientiane Delegation Returns From China </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Vientiane Delegation Returns From China </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK0306141594 Vientiane KPL in English 0930 GMT 3 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> BK0306141594 </F>
<F P=104>  Vientiane KPL </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Vientiane, June 3 (KPL) -- Vientiane Mayor 
Boun-gnang Volachit, who led a Lao delegation of 20 members to 
visit China since May 19, returned home yesterday. 
  The purpose of the Lao delegation's visit was to attend a 
seminar to share experience on economic development as well as 
investment opportunities with its Chinese counterparts, 
particularly after China opened up its door to the outside world. 
  The Lao senior officials also presented to the seminar the 
renovation policy of Laos for discussions and experience 
exchanges. 

</TEXT>

