<F P=102>   BK0606075194 Hanoi VNA in English 0646 GMT 6 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> BK0606075194 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi VNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Hanoi VNA June 6 -- A delegation of the Communist 
Party of Vietnam Central Committee led by Nguyen Van Hon, member 
of the CPV CC, paid a five-day visit to Cuba from May 30, the 
last leg of its Latin America visit. 
  While in Cuba, the Vietnamese delegation had working 
sessions 
with senior officials of the Cuban Communist Party's Foreign 
Relations Committee and the Cuban-Vietnam Friendship 
Association. It was received by Jose Ramon Balaguer, Politburo 
member of the Cuban Communist Party (CCP) and in charge of 
ideology and external relations. 
  Host and guest affirmed the wishes of the parties and 
Governments of Vietnam and Cuba for further strengthening and 
developing the friendship, solidarity and multiform cooperation 
between two the countries. 

</TEXT>

