  [Text] Vienna, 2 May (KYODO) -- Councilor Yun Ho-chin of 
the DPRK (North Korean) Embassy in Vienna stated the following 
on 2 June: We will have to formally withdraw from the Nuclear 
Nonproliferation Treaty (NPT) if the International Atomic Energy 
