<H3> <TI>   Ambassador to Thailand Supports ARF </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Ambassador to Thailand Supports ARF </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK0306101394 Hanoi VNA in English 0619 GMT 3 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> BK0306101394 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi VNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Hanoi VNA June 6 -- Vietnamese Ambassador to 
Thailand Le Cong Phung on Wednesday reiterated Vietnam's support 
for the ASEAN's initiative to held the ASEAN Regional Forum 
(ARF) to create a favourable atmosphere for regional development 
and cooperation. 
  After stresssing on the timeliness and vitality of the 
initiative the ambassdor said that Vietnam over the past years 
constantly pursued its comprehensive renovation policy, a 
priority of which was given to expanding international 
cooperation, and that Vietnam always wished that foreign 
investors and entrepreneurs would further promote their 
investment and business in Vietnam. 
  The forum is expected to be held in Bangkok in July. 

</TEXT>

