<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    MITI Chief Sees `Bright' Signals in Economy </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW0706022194 Tokyo KYODO in English 0217 GMT 7 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW0706022194 </F>
