  [Text] The visiting premier of South Australia, Mr. Dean 
Brown, today called on Prime Minister Goh Chok Tong and 
Environment and Communications Minister Mah Bow Tan. During the 
meeting, Mr. Brown discussed opportunities for Australian and 
Singapore companies to go regional together, especially in China. 
